{"tid":97424,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"辦 年 貨 被 女 圍  坤 哥：幾 多 女 埋 我 身","createTime":"2017-01-27T15:42:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-30T21:30:30.000Z","uid":35964,"like":4,"dislike":254,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8fb93cee9b14f0b0ec3b99a105ccd7ea5489fb46","tid":97424,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T15:42:11.000Z","msg":"吳業坤（坤哥）近年人氣爆燈，趁農曆新年將至，他做孝順仔為媽媽辦年貨。他走到傳統街市糖果店，細心選購糖果放全盒，大受婆婆、師奶及小女孩歡迎，爭先要跟坤哥合照留念，帶旺全場，非常熱鬧。<br />\n坤哥早前帶同《明報》讀者一齊去街市辦年貨，他說：「辦年貨多數由媽媽來做，我今年就試試負責買糖果放全盒，我最鍾意選金色的朱古力，一打開全盒金光閃閃，相當有霸氣。」<br />\n<br />\n市民索合照有求必應<br />\n坤哥現身街市，吸引不少師奶注目，不時尖叫「坤哥，你好靚仔呀」、「坤哥我支持你」、「你唱歌好好聽呀」。當他遇到一位4歲小妹妹，即時捉實對方一齊選糖果，沒想到小妹妹像專家一樣逐款向坤哥介紹，且一邊買一邊試食，大快朵頤。當坤哥將糖果裝到「盆滿砵滿」後，見到不少在場的街坊支持，他決定請大家「抓銀」兼嘗「甜頭」，向大家派糖果，與眾同樂。坤哥派糖之餘亦不忘向大家「硬銷」其新專輯，又提醒記得留意2月份播出的劇集《迷》，希望大家多多支持，非常搞笑。<br />\n<br />\n望增人緣 不恨拍拖<br />\n屬馬的坤哥透露自己今年犯太歲，他會依足中國傳統文化去拜神攝太歲，希望一切平安。新年打算去日本旅行度歲，放鬆一下。問到雞年會否想有桃花運？坤哥笑稱不一定要拍拖，心想要更好的人緣，打好人際關係或跟圈中不同的人多合作。今次街市行吸納不少女粉絲，坤哥自詡說：「我都話我桃花旺啦！你見幾多女埋我身？厲害吧！哈哈，真的多謝大家的支持，被大家包圍的感覺很幸福，祝福大家新一年都身體健康，開開心心！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20170127/s00092/974f3bc1ebb4921181c54707b5b4c1b5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20170127%2Fs00092%2F974f3bc1ebb4921181c54707b5b4c1b5.jpg&h=5ac5ee27&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ec6e9bad6feb1c5e43c482bf77b542c8e6487a7d","tid":97424,"uid":53011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T15:43:13.000Z","msg":"負評 上一頁"},{"pid":"ae180c43c78113a755318b02ce0f0082a2c1ab1f","tid":97424,"uid":1085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T20:37:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8a63a149acca38fe4761c7ae744ab8d2b0ef666d","tid":97424,"uid":71449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T20:39:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0v14uH9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0v14uH9.jpg&h=1ceeb655&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪撚放大啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df6a5ce879b1e38a1c416e6c0e86807e80098232","tid":97424,"uid":43190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T20:41:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0v14uH9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0v14uH9.jpg&h=1ceeb655&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"235cae4372483db3b19a4757494be8620b3a781d","tid":97424,"uid":37281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T23:31:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c98ddc6f7743bbdbd9f354d5f6ac295253f82dc5","tid":97424,"uid":14816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T04:42:52.000Z","msg":"佢係咪諗住自嘲 最後柒多鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb8c51e0fb88687560ecfeeca6e868112ca9beb1","tid":97424,"uid":1256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T04:50:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢係咪諗住自嘲 最後柒多鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n柒少陣當幫忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c4cacb07a0acf862c29b29496b83c929dc160d5","tid":97424,"uid":43804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T04:57:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://na.cx/i/0v14uH9.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0v14uH9.jpg&d=WR3KeWjj0JuqOJLXqtgwAAT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=b0ce9804\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/0v14uH9.jpg</a></blockquote><br />\n咪撚放大啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"852919a66453db5a91d4a695d56258aab8874e65","tid":97424,"uid":76112